Revenue Growth:
Revenue Growth = (Current Month BCM - Last 3 Months Avg BCM)/(Last 3 Months Avg BCM)

"Negative growth = 0-30 points (Capped at -5%)
0-5% growth = 31-60 points
5-15% growth = 61-80 points
15%+ growth = 81-100 points" (Capped at 25%)
Renewal Urgency Months:
Renewal Urgency = Days to deplete / days to renewal 
Days to deplete = (effective_acr*contract_length in years - ctd) / (Last 3 months Avg BCM)
User Activation %: Product Utilization Rate = Number of features used / Total no of features in the org
User Stickiness:
User Stickiness Ratio = Daily Active Users (r7d) / 
Monthly Active Users (r30d)
Product Stickiness: Product Utilization Rate = Number of features used / Total no of features in the org
OVERAGES:
Overages % = (MTD - min commit amt)/(min commit amt)

Score = 1/log(1+x) where x = overages %
Contract Length (months):
Contract Length = Total number of years of contract 

"0 months (month-to-month) = 25 points
12 months = 50 points
24 months = 75 points
36+ months = 100 points"
